[2026-02-24 19:05:00] Task ID: 接入与路由模块_001
Status: SUCCESS
Description: Implement SessionManager for IM route binding and cascade destruction

Implementation Summary:
- Created SessionManager interface with 5 methods:
  * bindOrCreateTaskSession(imType, imGroupId, topic) - creates or gets bound internal Master Task ID
  * getInternalTaskId(imType, imGroupId) - finds internal task ID by external group ID
  * destroySessionCascade(imGroupId) - handles cascade deletion when group is dissolved
  * hasBinding(imType, imGroupId) - checks if binding exists
  * getBindingCount() - returns total binding count
- Created SessionManagerImpl with:
  * ConcurrentHashMap for storing binding mapping (key: "imType:imGroupId", value: masterSessionId)
  * TaskManager injection for creating Master tasks
  * TaskSessionRepository injection for finding child sessions
  * SingleThreadDbWriter injection for submitting deletion events
  * bindOrCreateTaskSession implementation:
    - Checks if binding already exists, returns if valid
    - Creates new Master task via TaskManager.createMasterTask()
    - Removes stale bindings when session no longer exists
  * destroySessionCascade implementation:
    - Finds all matching bindings across IM types by imGroupId
    - Queries all Worker sessions via TaskSessionRepository.findByParentId()
    - Submits DeleteMessagesEvent and DeleteTaskSessionEvent for all workers
    - Submits DeleteMessagesEvent and DeleteTaskSessionEvent for master
    - Removes binding from memory map

Key Design Features:
- Thread-safe using ConcurrentHashMap for binding storage
- Binding key format: "imType:imGroupId" (e.g., "FEISHU:oc_123456")
- Supports multiple IM platforms with same group ID
- Automatic stale binding cleanup when session no longer exists
- Cascade deletion handles all Worker child sessions before Master
- Comprehensive parameter validation and error handling
- SLF4J logging for debugging and monitoring

Test Results: 32/32 tests passed (100%)
- 4 constructor validation tests
- 9 bindOrCreateTaskSession tests (new, existing, stale, multiple, parameter validation)
- 6 getInternalTaskId tests (success, parameter validation, binding not found)
- 5 destroySessionCascade tests (with workers, no workers, multiple IM types, parameter validation)
- 4 hasBinding tests (true, false, null parameters)
- 4 getBindingCount tests (zero, increment, decrement)

